data.text:
Hi @gillianoberholzer 

We need to clarify what fields are needed by Transunion for Debt Reviews.
For Debt Reviews there are no Defendants and Plaintiffs, hence the extract file might be a new file as we would need to cater for the below data:

Applicants,
Applicants Expense,
Creditors,
Debt Counselors

@cobuspienaar
